  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-The war against the Comic Dark was lost, now the few survivors are trapped. Warren stands up to continue the fight assisted by a mysterious golden light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Explore a segmented open world and clear out the dark by defeating enemies, bosses, or destroying galls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Find and collect treasure and coin left behind in the war, then use it to buy armor or level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Enter caves and dungeons, explore its depths, then defeat the boss at the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Learn new magic abilities, powerful attacks that consume MP and stun enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Clear enough of the dark from the area to fight the Area Boss, then defeat it to unlock the next segment of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A dynamic time of day and weather system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Estimated play time is about 5-7 hours.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-The war against the Comic Dark was lost, now the few survivors are trapped. Warren stands up to continue the fight assisted by a mysterious golden light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Explore a segmented open world and clear out the dark by defeating enemies, bosses, or destroying galls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Find and collect treasure and coin left behind in the war, then use it to buy armor or level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Enter caves and dungeons, explore its depths, then defeat the boss at the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Learn new magic abilities, powerful attacks that consume MP and stun enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Clear enough of the dark from the area to fight the Area Boss, then defeat it to unlock the next segment of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-A dynamic time of day and weather system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Estimated play time is about 5-7 hours.</p>",
